 \"reason\": \"jackrabbit-webdav 2.0-beta4 declares servlet-api as provided, and core WebDAV server, request, response, header, and I/O classes reference javax.servlet/javax.servlet.http types; existing tests for 1.5.0 already add this dependency explicitly.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No Docker image, external WebDAV server, Jackrabbit repository, environment variable, or system property is required. Prefer in-process tests over integration setup: exercise XML parsing/serialization, WebDAV method classes, locators, properties, reports, headers, and server abstractions with simple test doubles for servlet request/response objects where needed. Use javax.servlet APIs, not jakarta.servlet.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The library is only a WebDAV utility/server/client library; tests that try to run the Jackrabbit webapp or a real repository would add unnecessary setup.\",\n    \"The existing native-image run failure appears tied to generated test behavior/version drift rather than missing external infrastructure; local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0cbf26a2732a2986016a4286896dac81979aaa09e45bac8547\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 747, "output": 698, "cacheRead": 31232, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 32677, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782744704363, "responseId": "resp_0cbf26a2732a2986016a428680defc819786d2d2b766d7a82f"}}
